description: I invited young bodybuilder Zack to inaugurate my new home gym. Zack is 3 weeks away from his bodybuilding competition so I thought it would be nice to follow his progress. You'll agree watching Zack strip that he will be a strong contender. He has never been this cut (less than 4.5% body fat). No need to say that it is a great source of motivation to watch a hot guy like Zack lie down on my bench press. I imagine all sorts of things happening in my home gym in a near future...
title: Home Gym Inauguration
